<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="长连接业务测试 - WebSocket / SSE / 长轮询">
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 16 16%22><text y=%2214%22 font-size=%2214%22>🔌</text></svg>">
    <title>长连接业务测试 - 负载均衡测试站点</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/info.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/status.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
    <style>
        .lc-container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .ws-interval { width: 120px; }
        .lp-wait     { width: 140px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container lc-container">
        <h1>🔌 长连接业务测试</h1>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">🖥️ 当前服务器IP</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= serverIP %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">⏰ 当前时间</div>
                <div class="info-value live-clock"><%= currentTime %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">🔑 会话ID</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= sessionId %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item <%= faultMode === 'none' ? 'info-item--ok' : 'info-item--down' %>">
                <div class="info-label">🎯 本Pod故障状态</div>
                <div class="info-value">
                    <% if (faultMode === 'none') { %>
                        <span class="badge badge--ok">正常</span>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <span class="badge badge--down">已注入：<%= faultMode %></span>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>📊 实时连接统计</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-num" id="stat-ws">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">WebSocket 连接数</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-num" id="stat-sse">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">SSE 连接数</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-num" id="stat-lp">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">长轮询连接数</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="note">实时通过 SSE 推送（仅本 Pod 的统计，连接事件触发时立即更新）。</div>

        <h2>1️⃣ WebSocket 长连接</h2>
        <div class="card">
            <p>建立到 <code>ws://&lt;host&gt;/ws</code> 的 WebSocket 连接，可发送任意消息，服务器会回显并周期性推送 tick。可用于测试 F5 的 WebSocket 透传、连接保持时长、OneConnect 等。</p>
            <div class="form-row">
                <label>推送间隔 (ms):</label>
                <input type="number" id="ws-interval" class="ws-interval" value="2000" min="500" step="500">
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-success" id="ws-connect">🔌 建立连接</button>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" id="ws-disconnect" disabled>❌ 断开</button>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <label>消息内容:</label>
                <input type="text" id="ws-msg" placeholder="输入消息，回车发送..." style="flex:1;max-width:400px;" disabled>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" id="ws-send" disabled>📨 发送</button>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <label><input type="checkbox" id="ws-auto-send" disabled> 自动发送</label>
                <label>间隔 (ms):</label>
                <input type="number" id="ws-auto-interval" class="ws-interval" value="3000" min="500" step="500" disabled>
                <span class="note" id="ws-auto-status">已发送: 0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">🔗 连接ID</div><div class="info-value" id="ws-conn-id">—</div></div>
                <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">🖥️ 连接Pod IP</div><div class="info-value" id="ws-conn-ip">—</div></div>
                <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">🔐 协议</div><div class="info-value" id="ws-proto">—</div></div>
                <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">📨 总消息数</div><div class="info-value" id="ws-msg-count">0</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="log-area" id="ws-log">等待连接...</div>
        </div>

        <h2>2️⃣ Server-Sent Events (SSE)</h2>
        <div class="card">
            <p>建立到 <code>/sse</code> 的 SSE 连接，服务器周期性推送事件。用于测试 F5 的 HTTP 长连接 / chunked 响应保持。</p>
            <div class="form-row">
                <label>推送间隔 (ms):</label>
                <input type="number" id="sse-interval" class="ws-interval" value="1000" min="500" step="500">
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-success" id="sse-connect">📡 建立连接</button>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" id="sse-disconnect" disabled>❌ 断开</button>
            </div>
            <div class="log-area" id="sse-log">等待连接...</div>
        </div>

        <h2>3️⃣ HTTP 长轮询</h2>
        <div class="card">
            <p>向 <code>/long-poll?wait=&lt;ms&gt;</code> 发起请求，服务器阻塞指定毫秒后才响应。可测试 F5 的连接池管理、长连接超时、空闲连接清理等。</p>
            <div class="form-row">
                <label>等待时长 (ms, 最多 120000):</label>
                <input type="number" id="lp-wait" class="lp-wait" value="30000" min="1000" max="120000" step="1000">
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" id="lp-start">🚀 发起长轮询</button>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" id="lp-abort" disabled>🛑 取消</button>
            </div>
            <div class="log-area" id="lp-log">等待请求...</div>
        </div>

        <h2>ℹ️ F5 长连接测试说明</h2>
        <div class="card">
            <ul>
                <li><strong>WebSocket</strong>：F5 透传 WS 升级请求，连接会一直保持。建议在 F5 上配置 <em>OneConnect</em> profile，并观察 F5 是否会主动断开空闲 WS。</li>
                <li><strong>SSE</strong>：HTTP 响应保持打开状态，content-type 为 <code>text/event-stream</code>。可验证 F5 是否会按 idle timeout 强制关闭。</li>
                <li><strong>长轮询</strong>：请求在服务器上 hold 住 N 秒。观察 F5 的连接池复用、超时阈值是否合理。</li>
                <li><strong>多 Pod 验证</strong>：连续刷新本页或多次建立连接，观察 <em>当前服务器IP</em>，验证 F5 是否按预期将不同长连接分发到不同 Pod。</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-lg">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary">🏠 返回主页</a>
            <a href="/admin/fault" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">⚙️ 故障注入管理</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/clock.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/logger.js"></script>
    <script>
    // ---------------- Stats via SSE (替代原 2s 轮询) ----------------
    function updateStats(ws, sse, lp) {
        document.getElementById('stat-ws').textContent = ws || 0;
        document.getElementById('stat-sse').textContent = sse || 0;
        document.getElementById('stat-lp').textContent = lp || 0;
    }
    // 订阅 /api/fault/stream，复用同一个 SSE 通道（type === 'conn_stats' 时只更新统计）
    try {
        const statsEs = new EventSource('/api/fault/stream');
        statsEs.onmessage = (ev) => {
            try {
                const msg = JSON.parse(ev.data);
                if (msg.type === 'conn_stats' && msg.stats) {
                    updateStats(msg.stats.websocket, msg.stats.sse, msg.stats.longPoll);
                }
            } catch (e) { /* ignore */ }
        };
        statsEs.onerror = () => { /* EventSource 自动重连 */ };
    } catch (e) { /* EventSource 不支持 */ }

    // ---------------- Loggers (复用 makeLogger) ----------------
    const wsAppend = makeLogger('ws-log');
    const sseAppend = makeLogger('sse-log');
    const lpAppend = makeLogger('lp-log');

    // ---------------- WebSocket ----------------
    // 注意：WebSocket 不会自动重连。设计意图是让用户观察 F5 action on service down
    // 为 drop 时的行为——F5 静默丢包，客户端 TCP 层既收不到 RST 也收不到 FIN，
    // 只有 TCP keepalive 超时后连接才会断开。不自动重连可以清晰观察这一过程。
    let ws = null;
    let wsConnId = '';
    let wsMsgCount = 0;
    let wsAutoTimer = null;   // 自动发送的 setInterval ID
    let wsAutoCount = 0;       // 自动发送计数器

    function buildWsUrl() {
        const interval = document.getElementById('ws-interval').value || 2000;
        const proto = location.protocol === 'https:' ? 'wss' : 'ws';
        return `${proto}://${location.host}/ws?interval=${interval}`;
    }

    function setWsButtons(connected) {
        document.getElementById('ws-connect').disabled = connected;
        document.getElementById('ws-disconnect').disabled = !connected;
        document.getElementById('ws-send').disabled = !connected;
        document.getElementById('ws-msg').disabled = !connected;
        document.getElementById('ws-auto-send').disabled = !connected;
        document.getElementById('ws-auto-interval').disabled = !connected;
        if (!connected) {
            stopAutoSend();
            document.getElementById('ws-auto-send').checked = false;
            document.getElementById('ws-auto-status').textContent = '已发送: 0';
        }
    }

    function updateWsInfo(id, serverIP) {
        document.getElementById('ws-conn-id').textContent = id || '—';
        document.getElementById('ws-conn-ip').textContent = serverIP || '—';
        document.getElementById('ws-msg-count').textContent = wsMsgCount;
    }

    function sendWsMessage(fromAuto) {
        if (!ws || ws.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) return;
        let msg;
        if (fromAuto) {
            wsAutoCount++;
            msg = '[auto #' + wsAutoCount + '] ' + new Date().toISOString();
            document.getElementById('ws-auto-status').textContent = '已发送: ' + wsAutoCount;
        } else {
            msg = document.getElementById('ws-msg').value.trim();
            if (!msg) {
                msg = 'hello at ' + new Date().toISOString();
            }
            document.getElementById('ws-msg').value = '';
        }
        ws.send(msg);
        wsMsgCount++;
        document.getElementById('ws-msg-count').textContent = wsMsgCount;
        wsAppend((fromAuto ? '🔄 ' : '➡ ') + msg, 'log-ws');
    }

    function startAutoSend() {
        if (wsAutoTimer) return;
        const interval = Math.max(500, parseInt(document.getElementById('ws-auto-interval').value, 10) || 3000);
        wsAutoTimer = setInterval(() => sendWsMessage(true), interval);
        wsAppend('🔄 自动发送已启动 (间隔 ' + interval + 'ms)', 'log-ws');
    }

    function stopAutoSend() {
        if (wsAutoTimer) {
            clearInterval(wsAutoTimer);
            wsAutoTimer = null;
            wsAppend('⏸ 自动发送已停止 (共发送 ' + wsAutoCount + ' 条)', 'log-ws');
        }
    }

    function connectWs() {
        if (ws) return;
        wsAutoCount = 0;
        const url = buildWsUrl();
        // 显示实际使用的 WebSocket 协议（ws=明文, wss=TLS加密）
        document.getElementById('ws-proto').textContent = url.startsWith('wss') ? 'WSS (TLS加密)' : 'WS (明文)';
        wsAppend(`正在连接 ${url} ...`, 'log-ws');
        ws = new WebSocket(url);
        ws.onopen = () => {
            wsAppend('✅ 连接已建立，等待服务端欢迎消息...', 'log-ws');
            setWsButtons(true);
            document.getElementById('ws-msg').focus();
            // 如果连接前已经勾了自动发送，自动启动
            if (document.getElementById('ws-auto-send').checked) {
                startAutoSend();
            }
        };
        ws.onmessage = (ev) => {
            wsMsgCount++;
            document.getElementById('ws-msg-count').textContent = wsMsgCount;
            try {
                const data = JSON.parse(ev.data);
                // welcome 消息：提取连接 ID 和服务器 IP
                if (data.type === 'welcome') {
                    wsConnId = data.id;
                    updateWsInfo(data.id, data.serverIP);
                    wsAppend(`👋 欢迎 [${data.id}] Pod=${data.serverIP} client=${data.clientIP}`, 'log-ws');
                    return;
                }
                // echo 消息：服务器回显（request-response 复用同一连接）
                if (data.type === 'echo') {
                    wsAppend(`⬅ echo [#${data.seq}] Pod=${data.serverIP} preview="${data.echoPreview}"`, 'log-ws');
                    return;
                }
                // tick 消息：服务器主动推送
                if (data.type === 'tick') {
                    wsAppend(`⬅ tick [#${data.seq}] Pod=${data.serverIP} time=${data.time}`, 'log-ws');
                    return;
                }
                // fault 消息：故障注入导致服务端暂停/恢复 tick
                if (data.type === 'fault') {
                    if (data.action === 'pause') {
                        wsAppend(`⏸ 故障注入 (${data.mode})，服务端 tick 已暂停 — 模拟双方静默状态`, 'log-error');
                    } else if (data.action === 'resume') {
                        wsAppend('▶ 故障恢复 (none)，服务端 tick 已恢复', 'log-ws');
                    }
                    return;
                }
            } catch (e) { /* not JSON */ }
            // 非 JSON 或无法解析的消息
            wsAppend('⬅ ' + ev.data, 'log-ws');
        };
        ws.onerror = (e) => wsAppend('⚠ error: ' + (e.message || e), 'log-error');
        ws.onclose = (ev) => {
            stopAutoSend();
            wsAppend(`🔌 连接关闭 code=${ev.code} reason="${ev.reason || ''}"`, 'log-ws');
            updateWsInfo('(已断开)', '(已断开)');
            document.getElementById('ws-proto').textContent = '—';
            ws = null;
            wsConnId = '';
            setWsButtons(false);
            // 不做自动重连：F5 执行 action on service down=drop 时静默丢包，
            // 客户端可能很久才会感知（TCP keepalive 超时或发送数据时发现）。
            // 如需重新建立连接，请手动点击「建立连接」按钮。
        };
    }

    document.getElementById('ws-connect').onclick = () => {
        connectWs();
    };
    document.getElementById('ws-disconnect').onclick = () => {
        if (ws) ws.close();
    };
    document.getElementById('ws-send').onclick = () => {
        sendWsMessage(false);
    };
    document.getElementById('ws-msg').addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
        if (e.key === 'Enter') {
            e.preventDefault();
            sendWsMessage(false);
        }
    });
    // 自动发送开关
    document.getElementById('ws-auto-send').addEventListener('change', function() {
        if (this.checked) {
            startAutoSend();
        } else {
            stopAutoSend();
        }
    });
    // 自动发送间隔变更时，如果正在运行则重启
    document.getElementById('ws-auto-interval').addEventListener('change', function() {
        if (wsAutoTimer) {
            stopAutoSend();
            startAutoSend();
        }
    });

    // ---------------- SSE ----------------
    let es = null;
    document.getElementById('sse-connect').onclick = () => {
        if (es) return;
        const interval = document.getElementById('sse-interval').value || 1000;
        sseAppend(`正在连接 /sse?interval=${interval} ...`, 'log-sse');
        es = new EventSource(`/sse?interval=${interval}`);
        es.onopen = () => {
            sseAppend('✅ SSE 已建立', 'log-sse');
            document.getElementById('sse-connect').disabled = true;
            document.getElementById('sse-disconnect').disabled = false;
        };
        es.onmessage = (ev) => {
            sseAppend('⬅ ' + ev.data, 'log-sse');
        };
        es.onerror = () => {
            sseAppend('⚠ SSE 错误 (可能连接已断开)', 'log-error');
            es.close();
            es = null;
            document.getElementById('sse-connect').disabled = false;
            document.getElementById('sse-disconnect').disabled = true;
        };
    };
    document.getElementById('sse-disconnect').onclick = () => {
        if (es) { es.close(); es = null; }
        document.getElementById('sse-connect').disabled = false;
        document.getElementById('sse-disconnect').disabled = true;
    };

    // ---------------- Long Poll ----------------
    let lpCtrl = null;
    document.getElementById('lp-start').onclick = () => {
        if (lpCtrl) return;
        const wait = Math.max(1000, Math.min(120000, parseInt(document.getElementById('lp-wait').value, 10) || 30000));
        lpAppend(`发起 /long-poll?wait=${wait} ...`, 'log-lp');
        const start = Date.now();
        lpCtrl = new AbortController();
        fetch(`/long-poll?wait=${wait}`, { signal: lpCtrl.signal })
            .then(r => r.json())
            .then(d => {
                lpAppend(`✅ 响应：实际 ${Date.now() - start} ms，${JSON.stringify(d)}`, 'log-lp');
            })
            .catch(e => {
                lpAppend(`❌ ${e.name}: ${e.message}`, 'log-error');
            })
            .finally(() => {
                lpCtrl = null;
                document.getElementById('lp-start').disabled = false;
                document.getElementById('lp-abort').disabled = true;
            });
        document.getElementById('lp-start').disabled = true;
        document.getElementById('lp-abort').disabled = false;
    };
    document.getElementById('lp-abort').onclick = () => {
        if (lpCtrl) lpCtrl.abort();
    };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
